<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A Geometry type is used to group a list of Attribute objects together to form a geometric shape Qt3D is able to render using <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-render-geometryrenderer.xml">GeometryRenderer</db:link>. Special attribute can be set in order to calculate bounding volume of the shape.</db:para>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="property-documentation">
<db:title>Property Documentation</db:title>
<db:section xml:id="attributes-prop">
<db:title>attributes : list&lt;Attribute&gt;</db:title>
<db:fieldsynopsis>
<db:type>list&lt;Attribute&gt;</db:type>
<db:varname>attributes</db:varname>
<db:modifier>writable</db:modifier>
<db:synopsisinfo role="access">public</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="status">active</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="threadsafeness">unspecified</db:synopsisinfo>
</db:fieldsynopsis>
<db:para>Holds the list of attributes the geometry comprises of.</db:para>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="boundingVolumePositionAttribute-prop">
<db:title>boundingVolumePositionAttribute : Attribute</db:title>
<db:fieldsynopsis>
<db:type>Attribute</db:type>
<db:varname>boundingVolumePositionAttribute</db:varname>
<db:modifier>writable</db:modifier>
<db:synopsisinfo role="access">public</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="status">active</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="threadsafeness">unspecified</db:synopsisinfo>
</db:fieldsynopsis>
<db:para>Holds the attribute used to compute the bounding volume. The bounding volume is used internally for picking and view frustum culling.</db:para>
<db:para>If unspecified, the system will look for the attribute using the name returned by QAttribute::defaultPositionAttributeName.</db:para>
